      <li class="col-span-12 sm--col-span-6 md--col-span-4">
        <h4 class="mt-0 font-sans uppercase text-grey-800 h5">VPRI Competitions + Initiatives</h4>
        <a href="/vpri-competitions-initiatives" class="block pt-2 text-sm no-underline">Learn about VPRI strategic campus-wide competitions and
          initiatives <svg role="img" class="inline-block w-6 h-6">
            <use xlink:href="#icon-caret"></use>
          </svg></a>
      </li>
      <li class="col-span-12 sm--col-span-6 md--col-span-4">
        <h4 class="mt-0 font-sans uppercase text-grey-800 h5">About VPRI</h4>
        <a href="/about-vpri" class="block pt-2 text-sm no-underline">Who's who in the VP Research + Innovation Office <svg role="img"
